
*** Introduction

niwpodcastdownloader uses the Qt framework version 4. However it does not use
the Qt gui. This is a console application.

It is designed to run on any operating system supported by Qt


*** Requirements

CMake >= 2.6.0
Qt 4 >= 4.4.0
Qt 4 SQLite module
SQLite 3


*** Platform Specic Code

Platform specific code can be disabled on a supported platform by specifiying
-D NO_PLATFORM=TRUE as part of the cmake configuation.

Platform specific code is used by deafult on:
* Linux
* Unix
* Window


*** Compile

$ cmake ./
$ make


*** Install

$ make install
